    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you gain a +4 bonus on saving throws made against fear and a +1&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Natural-Armor-Bonus\">natural armor</a>&nbsp;bonus. At 9th level, you lose your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Light-Sensitivity-Ex-\">light sensitivity</a>, gain immunity to fear, and your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Natural-Armor-Bonus\">natural armor</a>&nbsp;bonus increases to +2.</p>",
